		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />*Maybe* it'll be damn cool. I think I have to wait it to be released and games making good option from it to be released to say if it rocks or if it sucks.
<br />But maybe they'd have better to offer both types of contoller, "classic" and "new", so game developpers could choose wich one to use.
<br />A "new" controller could be better in a fighting game, while an "old" one would be better in a strategy RPG. I wouldn't see my moving a stick in the air to move units on a gird and order them to attack enemy units. But I would to fight a virtual enemy.

		

